item.title: Where The Crawdads Sing by Delia Owens
item.description:
Welcome to Offscript the podcast where literature meets cinema every week. Join hosts Bri & Alli as they compare and contrast your favorite books with their movie adaptations. From classic tales to contemporary bestsellers, we dissect the creative choices that shape these narratives in both mediums.  

 

Tune in for insightful discussions and a lively exploration of the magic that happens when stories make the leap from page to screen... Feed: https://feeds.redcircle.com/c2e8be73-3198-42f0-be1b-0efeaf97ca5b
